Our Products

Specializing in security around the door, we furnish locks (both mechanical and electrical), door closers, exit devices, steel doors and frames. We're also breaking new technological ground with biometrics, special surfaces, video surveillance, wireless connectivity, cloud technology and other electronic safety solutions.









Better security starts with better conversations


Different people have different security needs. We tailor our approach to each situation and create products to work with other systems - furnishing a truly integrated solution.
As electronic and mechanical landscapes continue to converge, we are making the world safer by solving new problems in new ways - creating practical solutions and leading-edge products. At Allegion, better solutions start with listening and building relationships that reinvent security.













For business
Protect your assets and your bottomline. From time and attendance to access control, Allegion has a variety of products to improve the way you do business.
Learn more >







