Allegion: Redefining Security
Allegion helps keep people safe and secure where they live work and visit. With more than 25 brands sold globally we specialize in security around the doorway and adjacent area: everything from residential locks and portable security to commercial locks, exit devices, openers and closers, electronic access control and workforce productivity solutions.
 
