For Business

Keeping your assets secure.













Access control
Create smarter access control for your business with smart card and traditional proximity technology, as well as multi-technology readers.






Biometrics
Verify and recognize a person’s true identity with technology that uses the size and shape of a person’s hand.






Door control & closers
Setting the industry standard for quality, durability and innovation, Allegion has a door control and closer for any application.















Door trim & accessories
Make an entrance with Allegion’s line of trim and door accessories that give you the utmost flexibility and choice when it comes to décor.






Doors & frames
Devoted to the manufacturing, service and innovation of doors, frames and frame components, Allegion has a style to complement your commercial space.






Electronic locks
Complete your business’ security with innovative and market-leading wireless and offline electronic locks.















Exit devices
Find a variety of exit devices, including door closers, operator sets and trim.






Key systems
Designed to provide the highest level of security with our key systems.






Mechanical locks
Explore a wide range of products, styles, and finishes for schools, hospitals, commercial business and more.















Sanitary hardware
Stay healthier with germ-resistant metal.






Workforce productivity
Solutions for a more productive workplace, that encompass workforce management, time management, and strategic HR Consulting.















