Locations[edit]
Allegion plc is headquartered in Dublin, Ireland. Its regional offices for the Americas is in Carmel, Indiana, USA. Its European regional offices are in Faenza, Italy, and the company’s Asia headquarters are in Tower B of City Center of Shanghai in Shanghai, China.[4]
