Volatility and Risk
NAPCO Security Technologies has a beta of 0.53, indicating that its stock price is 47% less volatile than the S&P 500. Comparatively, Allegion PLC has a beta of 1.11, indicating that its stock price is 11% more volatile than the S&P 500. 
Analyst Ratings
This is a summary of recent ratings and price targets for NAPCO Security Technologies and Allegion PLC, as provided by MarketBeat. 



